    <div class="hero__description">
      <p>Creative License is an exploration of how rules shape the creative process.
      This site functions as both an archive and an active system—documenting outcomes while also allowing rules to operate in real time.
      Across the work, the craft, and the self, rules act as constraints, prompts, and interruptions. They guide decisions, limit control, and generate unexpected results.
      Nothing here is neutral. Every outcome is influenced by the conditions it was made under.</p>
